Class PlayfieldPanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • gui.PlayfieldPanel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Player, PlayfieldDisplay, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class PlayfieldPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements PlayfieldDisplay, Player
    The PlayfieldPanel consists of a field of buttons that can display the contents of a playfield. It also implements the Player interface to allow the user to interact with the program as a player.
